                      <p style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5em;">(Answers: 1. put off, 2. fill in, 3. hold on, 4. deal with, 5. called off, 6. hand in, 7. set up, 8. carry on, 9. work out)</p>
